To send email notifications for significant updates on user requests and transactions, we'll integrate an email service in our application. This will require us to manage email configuration and implement the logic to send emails when certain statuses change.

Epic Title: Real-time Status Updates and Notifications

We will:
1. Create a service for sending emails.
2. Extend the status update logic to send email notifications for significant events.
3. Ensure the application configuration includes necessary email settings.

Here are the steps:

1. Implement an email service.
2. Update the status controller to send email notifications.

